---
title: Odysseys
description: "Long-term explorations into AI, biology, philosophy, and the systematic mapping of human knowledge — by JD Ranpariya."
layout: layouts/base
section: "odysseys"
---

<section class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
  <header class="mb-16 space-y-4">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-ink">Odysseys</h1>
    <p class="text-lead text-ink-secondary max-w-xl">
      Ongoing explorations I don't expect to finish.
    </p>
  </header>

  <ol class="index-list list-none m-0 p-0">
    {%
      set items = [
        ["/odysseys/purpose/",                     "Purpose",                    "Compass for what I work on and why."],
        ["/odysseys/the-codex-of-understanding/",  "The Codex of Understanding", "Systematic mapping of what I'm learning."],
        ["/odysseys/reckoning-the-dead/",          "Reckoning the Dead",         "Unearthing greats lost to time."],
        ["/odysseys/the-alchemists-hearth/",       "The Alchemist's Hearth", "Kitchen experiments and what I learned from them."]
      ]
    %}
    {% for item in items %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ item[0] }}" class="index-row">
          <h2 class="index-row__title">{{ item[1] }}</h2>
          <p class="index-row__desc">{{ item[2] }}</p>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</section>
